{
  "stem": "1042.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then he called us after, when he had the news, that we gonna work as long as possible, you know, like all the other factories, what they work for the Wehrmacht, for the German army.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So you know, we couldn't tell this everything.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We knew, the-- the five of us, we knew about it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But to tell to 1,000 men and 300 women what's going on, it would be impossible, you know, because they would-- they wouldn't go out from bed.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They would cry, anyhow, they're going to kill me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we, the five, we knew about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And after the war, we told them, you know, what was it here, what-- what he prepared for us, Schindler.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So with the food, you know, we didn't get from the Gestapo from Krakow.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We didn't get food, or maybe some minimal that it was impossible to live on it and to work.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He find out that the partisans, they are not far from the bushes there around.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And whenever the German army is passing by, they run out from the holes there on horses, and they used to fight to kill some Germans.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the Germans, they killed them with the horses together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So Schindler find out that there are-- not far from the factory-- that there are killed horses.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He took-- because they were people, Polish people from Krakow, not Jews, what they used to go out to do something, you know, to prepare.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he took three, four boys from them, and the horses and a big buggy, and he used to come with three horses, killed horses, on the buggy.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we had people, they were real good cooks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took out, you know, like a cow after when she's killed, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They took off the-- the-- the skin from it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were cooking in the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, we had a soup, because that was-- we had the meat, so we had the soup.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had almost two pounds bread for 24 hours.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So you can imagine that we had meat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had the soup and a slice of bread.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we were really, you know, we were praying to God that it happened, you know, such-- you know, it's-- it's really, really hard to describe what a human being was able to do for us to keep us alive.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we were working still.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But sometimes at work, something happened, you know, with a finger that we put somewhere, and we were-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] were bleeding, the hands, or something fall down on a leg.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he made a big room, and four doctors were with us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was running for everything what was important to have in a room for the people, because they were checking in the morning, who needed, you know, this [INAUDIBLE], you know, this special kind if something happened that we had to keep the hand on this special kind.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "OK, everything we had what we needed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the doctors were working for us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sometimes somebody had a fever, so we had the other basement.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They put it down, they shouldn't be with those healthy people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we did really everything, whatever he-- he didn't ask that much, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were doing really a lot, but this, what he did for us, it was more than possible.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Impossible.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But that was-- that was the life there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he find a bakery, you know, where we used to get additional bread.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We shall not be very hungry, you know, because he did really the most what he could.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that-- that was it until May-- May the 8th, May the 8th.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But May the 7th--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'45.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "May the 7th, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] he asked-- he was asking us that a few from us supposed to go with him because he has to run away.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He is a German, you know, and he had papers as a Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it was-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we were a few.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't go with him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it was three boys and three girls.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They went with him because he knew that the Russians are already on the way to come to the factory.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was afraid they gonna kill him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they took the truck-- the Jewish boys-- and they went with him at night till the first station of the Russian officers there.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they came, and they introduced him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is Mr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Schindler.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What we are here-- we were here with him-- we, in Brnenec, were only with him nine months, nine, 10 months, but he had the factory before, so he had 500 people was working there for him also.",
      "word_count": 38
    }
  ],
